{
  "stem": "1753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 88.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their work was to collect the clothes and remove the gold and-- and-- and-- and cut, shave the-- the-- the heads, the hair, which was-- everything was collected.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, the Nazis made use out of everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about a few hundred yards before we got to that camp II, now we could see.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the first time when we arrived in Treblinka, we didn't know because the-- the cattle cars were closed, but now they're open.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the train stopped.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We would see all kinds of smoke and noise and commotion, stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What happened that we later on learned, there was an uprising of Treblinka II, which is very famous, which is documented in publications.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And in fact, how, in what manner, in what circumstances that Treblinka I and Treblinka II, the people that organized the operation, they were, in fact, aligned.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Which-- on which I will give you the details in a moment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we waited there, and afterwards we learned, as I just mentioned, there was an uprising, and they destroyed the gas chambers and everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from what I understand, several hundred people escaped, but most of them were ultimately recaptured and killed on the spot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From what I understand from Treblinka II right now, there are only three or four survivors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From my camp, Treblinka I, there are nine survivors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Actually, now it's only 8 from what I know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Were they all Jews, the people who--?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All Jews.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We're only speaking about Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So ultimately, about two hours, then we got a little closer.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
